---
const { phone = "+1 435-246-0401" } = Astro.props
import ButtonPrimary from "./ButtonPrimary.astro";
---

<section class="hero relative min-h-[clamp(28rem,70vh,52rem)] bg-black bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat pt-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] pb-[clamp(4rem,6vw,6rem)]" style="background-image: url('https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/UOMC/background-gorilla.webp')">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    
    <!-- Rebel Ape Logo -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/UOMC/rebel-ape-marketing-logo-white.png" 
        alt="Rebel Ape Marketing" 
        class="block w-[clamp(160px,60vw,380px)] h-auto"
        loading="eager" 
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="w-full max-w-[960px] text-center mt-6 mb-8 lg:mt-10 lg:mb-10">
      <h1 class="font-black text-center text-white text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem)] leading-tight mb-14 text-balance">
        <span class="text-white">Get </span>
        <span class="text-green-600">More Jobs </span>
        <span class="text-white">With This </span>
        <span class="text-green-600">Marketing Roadmap</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column content (text + booklet image) -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-10 w-full max-w-6xl items-start lg:[&>div:nth-child(1)]:order-1 [&>div:nth-child(1)]:order-2">
      
      <!-- Left column: Text -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-start">
        <h2 class="text-left text-white font-black text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-4 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-white">The</span> <span class="text-green-600">Ultimate Online Marketing</span>
          <span class="text-white">Checklist</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-white text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This system makes your marketing work – finally bringing your ads, SEO, and website together to generate consistent leads.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-white text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Most roofers don't need more traffic – they need better marketing flow. This roadmap reveals the exact steps to fix what's broken in your funnel, show up for high-intent searches, and turn browsers into booked jobs. You'll see how to capture more leads, follow up automatically, and build the authority that keeps your pipeline full – even during the slow season.
        </p>

        <!-- Bullet List Hero -->
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Fix conversion leaks on your landing pages</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Show up for "roof repair" &amp; "roof replacement" nearby</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Get steady leads even when storms slow down</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Turn Google searches into real conversations with optimized listings</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Automate follow-ups so you never lose another lead</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-[1.15rem] h-[1.15rem] rounded-full bg-green-500 text-black font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Build authority that makes homeowners choose you over competitors</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <ButtonPrimary />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: Image -->
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center lg:order-last">
        <img
          src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/UOMC/uomc-book.webp?width=1200&format=webp"
          alt="Ultimate Roofing Lead Generation Checklist booklet"
          width="1200"
          height="1600"
          class="block w-full max-w-2xl h-auto rounded-lg"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>